title: The Walking Dead
plot: Sheriff Deputy Rick Grimes gets shot and falls into a coma. When awoken he finds himself in a Zombie Apocalypse. Not knowing what to do he sets out to find his family, after he's done that, he gets connected to a group to become the leader. He takes charge and tries to help this group of people survive, find a place to live and get them food. This show is all about survival, the risks and the things you'll have to do to survive.
awards: Nominated for 1 Golden Globe. Another 78 wins & 223 nominations.
stars: Andrew Lincoln, Norman Reedus, Melissa McBride, Lauren Cohan
companies: American Movie Classics (AMC), Circle of Confusion, Valhalla Motion Pictures

trailer.title: The Walking Dead
trailer.videoDescription: We find our survivors trying to pick themselves up by their bootstraps following the destruction the Whisperers left in their wake. The years of struggle weigh upon them as past traumas surface, exposing their more vulnerable sides. As they question the state of humanity, the state of their collective community, and the states of their minds, will they find the inner strength to persevere with their lives, friendships, and group intact?
